{
  "groups": [
    {
      "title": "Installation",
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "install_title",
          "label": "Getting Started",
          "icon": "rocket",
          "content": "# ZYNQ\n\n## Installation\n\nZYNQ is a WebRTC + games framework.\nIt combines peer-to-peer communication with a game library system.\n\nNo backend required."
        },
        {
          "id": "install_script",
          "label": "Script Tag",
          "icon": "code",
          "content": "## Script Tag\n\nLoads ZYNQ globally into `window.ZYNQ`.\n\n```html\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/un-zynq/zynq-lib@1.1.1/index.min.js\"></script>\n```\n\nAfter loading:\n```js\nwindow.ZYNQ\n```"
        },
        {
          "id": "install_module",
          "label": "ES Module",
          "icon": "package",
          "content": "## ES Module (Side Effect Import)\n\nThis version only initializes global `window.ZYNQ`.\n\n```js\nimport \"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/un-zynq/zynq-lib@1.1.1/index.min.js\"\n```\n\nAfter import:\n```js\nwindow.ZYNQ.Peer\nwindow.ZYNQ.games\n```"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "title": "ZYNQ Games",
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "games_object",
          "label": "Game Object",
          "icon": "gamepad-2",
          "content": "## ZYNQ.games\n\n### Game Object Structure\n\nRepresents a single game entry.\n\n```ts\nGame {\n  name: string,\n  alias: string,\n  url: string,\n  thumb: string,\n  category?: string,\n  devices?: number[],\n\n  isSupported: boolean\n}\n```\n"
        },

        {
          "id": "games_state",
          "label": "State & Getters",
          "icon": "database",
          "content": "# ZYNQ\n\n## ZYNQ.games\n\n### State\n\n```ts\nconfig: {\n  src: string,\n  cdn: string\n}\n\nall: Game[]\nfiltered: Game[]\nfavorites: Set<string>\ndeviceType: number // 1: PC Touch, 2: PC No Touch, 3: Phone, 4: Tablet\nhistory: string[]\n```\n\n### Getters\n\n```ts\nlist: Game[]\ntotal: number\nfilteredCount: number\n```\n"
        },

        {
          "id": "games_methods",
          "label": "Methods",
          "icon": "cog",
          "children": [
            {
              "id": "games_init",
              "label": ".init()",
              "content": "## init(options?)\nLoads game database from CDN.\n\n```js\nawait ZYNQ.games.init()\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_search",
              "label": ".search()",
              "content": "## search(query)\nFilters games.\n\n```js\nZYNQ.games.search(\"alien\")\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_random",
              "label": ".random()",
              "content": "## random(limit)\nRandom subset.\n\n```js\nZYNQ.games.random(3)\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_get_random_one",
              "label": ".getRandomOne()",
              "content": "## getRandomOne()\nSingle random game.\n\n```js\nZYNQ.games.getRandomOne()\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_shuffle",
              "label": ".shuffle()",
              "content": "## shuffle()\nShuffle list.\n\n```js\nZYNQ.games.shuffle()\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_sort_by",
              "label": ".sortBy()",
              "content": "## sortBy(field)\nSort games.\n\n```js\nZYNQ.games.sortBy(\"name\")\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_sort_popularity",
              "label": ".sortByPopularity()",
              "content": "## sortByPopularity()\nSort by popularity.\n\n```js\nZYNQ.games.sortByPopularity()\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_get_by_alias",
              "label": ".getByAlias()",
              "content": "## getByAlias(alias)\nFind game.\n\n```js\nZYNQ.games.getByAlias(\"alien-hominid\")\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_get_by_category",
              "label": ".getByCategory()",
              "content": "## getByCategory(category)\nFilter by category.\n\n```js\nZYNQ.games.getByCategory(\"shooter\")\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_filter_supported",
              "label": ".filterSupported()",
              "content": "## filterSupported()\nOnly supported games.\n\n```js\nZYNQ.games.filterSupported()\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_filter_favorites",
              "label": ".filterFavorites()",
              "content": "## filterFavorites()\nOnly favorites.\n\n```js\nZYNQ.games.filterFavorites()\n```"
            },
            {
              "id": "games_toggle_favorite",
              "label": ".toggleFavorite()",
              "content": "## toggleFavorite(alias)\nToggle favorite state.\n\n```js\nZYNQ.games.toggleFavorite(\"alien-hominid\")\n```"
            },

            {
              "id": "games_history",
              "label": "History API",
              "content": "## History API\n\n### addToHistory(alias)\n```js\nZYNQ.games.addToHistory(\"alien-hominid\")\n```\n\n### getHistory()\n```js\nZYNQ.games.getHistory()\n```\n\n### clearHistory()\n```js\nZYNQ.games.clearHistory()\n```"
            },

            {
              "id": "games_utils",
              "label": "Utilities",
              "content": "## Utilities\n\n### reset()\n```js\nZYNQ.games.reset()\n```\n\n### isFavorite(alias)\n```js\nZYNQ.games.isFavorite(\"alien-hominid\")\n```"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },

